<br>
1) Give tells to specific guild leaders, or emails using the Members page on the CoG site. If you find an email that is no longer valid for a guild leader, let me know and I'll update the page. <br>
2) Use the Submit a Press Release form on the CoG web site. That thing helped me get more press for the CoG than you'd ever believe. Some of the sites on the list may not be valid any longer, but it still submits to EQ Vault and Everlore, I think. Post a release saying that you are trying to get non-VS rotation guilds together for this purpose. <br>
3) Post on here as well. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
